lines.text: Put your weight on it! Put your weight on it! Put your weight on it!
Call the AMB-YOO-LANCE, and tell them what he has HAY-AD!
It keeps poundin' poundin' poundin' in my brain. Shit!

[holding a shotgun on a criminal]
Move and I'll blow your Afro off!
Where are you Mister? Are you with us or just in our minds?
Well Kimbo looks like we got you for good this time. I'm going to personally see that you are locked up and the key is thrown away forever, you decrepit old stupid son of a bitch!
I see Stinger's got you everywhere, telephone man. I'm gonna see you don't ring no more bells.
